Module org.nasdanika.architecture.containers.kubernetes
Package org.nasdanika.architecture.containers.kubernetes

Interface KubernetesPackage

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.ENamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EPackage, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
KubernetesPackageImpl
public interface KubernetesPackage extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EPackage
The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent
  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each operation of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
See Also:
  • KubernetesFactory
